This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories, as it focuses on image and sentence matching. The use of a Long Short-Term Memory network (LSTM) also suggests that it may fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the attention mechanism used in the proposed model may relate to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
